	'476',
	'<p>The Under2 coalition is driven by a group of ambitious state and regional governments committed to keeping the global temperature rise well below 2 ° C.</p><p>The coalition consists of more than 220 governments representing more than 1.3 billion people and 43% of the world economy.</p><p>The Climate Group is the Secretariat of the Under2 Coalition and works with governments to accelerate climate action through three workflows.</p><p>2050 WAYS</p><p>Planning of the deep decarbonisation path: support to governments to develop solid medium and long-term emission reduction plans (2050) in line with the objectives of the Paris Climate Agreement.</p><p>Political action</p><p>Expanding innovative policy solutions: spreading the best climate policies today and supporting governments to develop new policies.</p><p>TRANSPARENCY</p><p>Integration of transparency: support governments to have the experience and systems necessary to accurately assess their emissions, track progress and ensure that policies remain adequate to meet climate objectives.</p>',
